        {
            "title": "全球市場關注伊朗停火協議,美元走弱",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NhDDm1QaWfUMJXqyB0nj2g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/eru_pound_dollar_M_1440050124.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 隨著伊朗停火協議最初兩週期限到期,全球金融市場正密切關注相關進展,分析師指出,貨幣走勢和投資者情緒取決於緊張局勢是緩和還是升級。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞銀集團(UBS)的一份新報告強調,自4月7日停火協議生效以來,油價下跌和股市企穩推動美元兌主要貨幣普遍走弱。外匯市場波動性也降至數月低點,反映出投資者對停火協議可能延長或轉變為長期協議持樂觀態度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著油價遠低於近期高點,股指接近高位,投資者似乎已為持續穩定做好準備。瑞銀指出,這種環境有利於\"套利交易\",即投資者以日圓等低收益貨幣借款,投資於收益率較高的資產。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ebe18f98-f7f0-3dd4-8001-a7f97768ed5b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">如果美國與伊朗之間的外交談判取得進展,分析師預計美元將進一步走弱,澳元等風險敏感型貨幣將表現更強勁。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管市場樂觀,瑞銀警告稱存在\"尾部風險\"情景,即衝突可能恢復或加劇。重大升級——例如美國部署地面部隊——可能引發市場急劇轉向風險規避,從而推高美元並增加貨幣波動性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鑑於目前波動性水平相對較低,該報告指出,對沖此類下行風險的成本相對較低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外,瑞銀對日圓維持看空立場,理由是預計日本央行將在全球不確定性下推遲加息。該行還表示,就業數據喜憂參半,使英國央行政策前景不明朗,儘管經濟學家預計2026年稍後將降息,這可能對英鎊構成壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%B5%B0%E5%BC%B1-203050764.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-24 05:05:37",
